  "page": "Lord Caswell (father of Lorent)",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Caswell\" title=\"House Caswell\"><img alt=\"House Caswell.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/2a/House_Caswell.svg/50px-House_Caswell.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/2/2a/House_Caswell.svg/75px-House_Caswell.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/2/2a/House_Caswell.svg/100px-House_Caswell.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\">Lord Caswell</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Caswell\" title=\"House Caswell\"><img alt=\"House Caswell.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/2a/House_Caswell.svg/50px-House_Caswell.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/2/2a/House_Caswell.svg/75px-House_Caswell.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/2/2a/House_Caswell.svg/100px-House_Caswell.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_Bitterbridge\" title=\"Lord of Bitterbridge\">Lord of Bitterbridge</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Caswell\" title=\"House Caswell\">House Caswell</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Reach\" title=\"Reach\">Reach</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Issue</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Lorent_Caswell\" title=\"Lorent Caswell\">Lorent Caswell</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li><li>Four daughters<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Lord Caswell</b> was the Lord of <a href=\"/index.php/Bitterbridge\" title=\"Bitterbridge\">Bitterbridge</a> and the head of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Caswell\" title=\"House Caswell\">House Caswell</a> during the reign of King <a href=\"/index.php/Aerys_II_Targaryen\" title=\"Aerys II Targaryen\">Aerys II Targaryen</a>. His given name is unknown.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lord_Caswell_(father_of_Lorent)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Old Lord Caswell was <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_Bitterbridge\" title=\"Lord of Bitterbridge\">Lord of Bitterbridge</a> when his son, <a href=\"/index.php/Lorent_Caswell\" title=\"Lorent Caswell\">Lorent</a>, took a <a href=\"/index.php/Longsword\" title=\"Longsword\">longsword</a> made by the castle's <a href=\"/index.php/Armorer\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Armorer\">armorer</a> for his own son, <a href=\"/index.php/Rolly_Duckfield\" title=\"Rolly Duckfield\">Rolly</a>. After taking revenge by wounding Lorent, Rolly fled the <a href=\"/index.php/Reach\" title=\"Reach\">Reach</a> for the exiles of the <a href=\"/index.php/Golden_Company\" title=\"Golden Company\">Golden Company</a>. After his death, Lorent succeeded him as Lord of Bitterbridge.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Family\">Family</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lord_Caswell_(father_of_Lorent)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Family\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div style=\"overflow:auto;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:separate;font: 90% sans-serif;\">\n<tbody><tr align=\"center\"><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"6\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"border: 2px solid black; padding: 0.2em;&#160;;\"><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Lord Caswell</a></td><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black\"><div style=\"width:2em;height:1em\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"6\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"border: 2px solid black; padding: 0.2em;&#160;;\">Unknown<br />wife</td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td></tr><tr align=\"cente